  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was just having an opportunity to read a book-- I'm not taking too much time-- a book that they issued, that I showed you last time, in Israel, 50 And I saw some pictures there.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was trying to make a connection between it-- would you repeat the question?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was your family's relationship with the non-Jewish--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I saw a-- a poem by Julian Tuwim.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, Julian Tuwim was the premiere poet of Poland right before World War II, during.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, he was in the United States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He survived here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he went back to Poland and became really the poet of Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I read his poem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so I don't know-- when you say connection with the-- with the Polish culture, Polish society, I'm not so sure that I understand the difference.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But if you're talking about Polish culture, definitely, not only connected, but probably contributing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in the poem, he makes a reference to Lodz, because it's in memory of Lodz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was born in Lodz, and so he writes about Lodz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, among other things, that he says, and there, where I started my life as a poet, what I was getting paid by a-- by a publisher, $0.02 per line.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it strikes me very strange, because the publisher was my father, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I kind of took exception to that, maybe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think my father-- what my father did tell me, that during World War I, he did invite Tuwin for dinner, because he was hungry.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
